WELCOME TO THE NEW MESSAGE BOARDS! <br>
  <br>
Greyternal Hawkquiem welcomes you!  We are a group DEDICATED to excellence (for the first month).  As new officers in this amazing guild that we created from the ruins of our old guild and anyone else we happened to see along the way that was unguilded, we are very pleased to be here.  Specifically because if this works out like it does with other spur-of-the-moment guilds, officers make out like BANDITS with the loot! HELLS YEAH! <br>
  <br>
/hugs self <br>
  <br>
Man I cannot WAIT to get some amazing loot so I can sell my character on Ebay like so many other people do.  It’s awesome to get as much as you can from the sweat of other players then sell it on Ebay.  Then I can use that cash that others earned me and buy cool things like….ohh…. cars and stuff.  People are so impressed by how cool I am.  They are! <br>
 <br> 
This is going to be so COOL.  And when I brag to that stupid bitch at Arby’s…THIS time she better have something nice to say or BAM, I'm gonna kick her up a notch.  When I told my mom SHE was impressed at least.  It’s hard to tell sometimes… she has a naturally sarcastic voice around me.  She has since I was very young, and I used to tell her about how cool I was ganking people with my posse in Ultima Online.  Very strange how it suddenly appeared one day… <br>
 <br> 
Anyway, here we are!  A new guild with big dreams and new hopes!  Just to kick off our <b><font size=4><font color=red>NEW GUILD</font></font></b> (editor please make this a really kick ass font so I look like I know HTMEL or whatever it is you geeks use) we decided to kill QUARM!  Yeah!!!!  Here are some pictures.  In one, this guy Finneus or something wouldn’t get out of my way.  I was like “WTF NOOB UR IN MYWAY” and he was like “??”…. Fuckin n00bz.  Behind him is Quarm though.<br>
